casebody.data:
No. 86,

Misc.

Orloff v. Willoughby, Commandant. David Rein for petitioner. Philip B. Perlman, then Solicitor General, and Acting Solicitor General Stern for respondent.

C. A. 9th Cir. Certiorari granted. The motion for leave to file brief of Committee to Prevent Abuse of Doctors’ Draft Act, as amicus curiae, is denied.
